程序包 org.cloudbus.cloudsim

类 VmSchedulerTimeShared

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.VmScheduler
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.VmSchedulerTimeShared
直接已知子类:
VmSchedulerTimeSharedOverSubscription
public class VmSchedulerTimeShared
extends VmScheduler
VmSchedulerTimeShared is a Virtual Machine Monitor (VMM) allocation policy that allocates one or more PEs from a PM to a VM, and allows sharing of PEs by multiple VMs. This class also implements 10% performance degradation due to VM migration. This scheduler does not support over-subscription. Each host has to use is own instance of a VmScheduler that will so schedule the allocation of host's PEs for VMs running on it.
从以下版本开始:
CloudSim Toolkit 1.0
